00:00:43,740 --> 00:00:44,840
<font color="yellow">teach me a lesson?</font>

15
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,510
<font color="yellow">Are you going to kill me?</font>

16
00:00:47,170 --> 00:00:49,140
