00:01:37,270 --> 00:01:40,840
<font color="yellow">you came back to Korea and became a construction manager.</font>

31
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:44,610
<font color="yellow">You're going to be humiliated if I tell people about that, right?</font>

32
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:48,170
<font color="yellow">You won over my grandmother and aunt,</font>

