<font color="yellow">And threaten me to kill me?</font>

41
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,310
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

42
00:02:14,170 --> 00:02:15,610
<font color="yellow">I won't talk about you any more.</font>

