99
00:06:52,370 --> 00:06:55,240
<font color="yellow">I'm going to live with you.</font>

100
00:06:58,770 --> 00:07:00,170
<font color="yellow">Okay. Okay.</font>

101
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,670
