00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:22,570
<font color="yellow">Grandpa.</font>

108
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:24,440
<font color="yellow">My pumpkin.</font>

109
00:07:26,570 --> 00:07:28,370
<font color="yellow">What brings you here, Father?</font>

