<font color="yellow">That's not what I meant.</font>

112
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:36,040
<font color="yellow">- Do you want some tea? - It's okay.</font>

113
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:38,440
<font color="yellow">I had it upstairs.</font>

114
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,740
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

115
00:07:41,370 --> 00:07:42,370
<font color="yellow">Ah In,</font>

116
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:45,840
<font color="yellow">great-grandma came downstairs.</font>

117
00:07:46,210 --> 00:07:48,970
<font color="yellow">She will love it if you sing for her.</font>

118
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,670
<font color="yellow">- She will give you some candy, too. - Okay.</font>

119
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:56,040
<font color="yellow">Mommy, can I go play with great-grandma?</font>

120
00:07:56,110 --> 00:07:58,110
<font color="yellow">Of course you can. Don't run.</font>

121
00:07:59,010 --> 00:08:00,010
<font color="yellow">Go, sweetie.</font>

122
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:08,710
<font color="yellow">It's tough, isn't it?</font>

