127
00:08:21,110 --> 00:08:23,110
<font color="yellow">you don't have to do that in front of me.</font>

128
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,440
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

129
00:08:49,940 --> 00:08:51,640
<font color="yellow">What's this, Father?</font>

