<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon managed to get money somewhere.</font>

139
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:20,370
<font color="yellow">He doesn't even have a job. Where did he get the money?</font>

140
00:09:21,010 --> 00:09:22,140
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

141
00:09:24,110 --> 00:09:25,310
<font color="yellow">It's good.</font>

142
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:28,440
<font color="yellow">Just keep it...</font>

143
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:30,740
<font color="yellow">and use it to pay the next month's rent.</font>

144
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,610
<font color="yellow">Get some snacks for the kids.</font>

145
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:38,940
<font color="yellow">Also, fill your grandmother's fridge with some food.</font>

146
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:42,440
<font color="yellow">Old people need to eat well.</font>

147
00:09:43,370 --> 00:09:45,640
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep crying?</font>

148
00:09:45,770 --> 00:09:47,510
<font color="yellow">Father,</font>

149
00:09:48,370 --> 00:09:49,910
<font color="yellow">I am so sorry.</font>

150
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:54,680
<font color="yellow">I am truly ashamed.</font>

151
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:57,640
<font color="yellow">I am sorry, Father.</font>

