00:39:49,370 --> 00:39:51,970
<font color="yellow">I'm listed on Aunt and Uncle's family registry.</font>

640
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:54,610
<font color="yellow">So why is it so bad about sleeping at Grandma's place?</font>

641
00:39:55,010 --> 00:39:57,910
<font color="yellow">How dare you speak to me like this?</font>

642
00:39:58,870 --> 00:40:00,070
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

643
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,370
<font color="yellow">I'll make money.</font>

644
00:40:03,410 --> 00:40:05,110
<font color="yellow">And I'll leave Korea again.</font>

645
00:40:08,610 --> 00:40:10,040
<font color="yellow">How could she...</font>

646
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:23,440
<font color="yellow">It's over there.</font>

647
00:40:39,040 --> 00:40:40,070
<font color="yellow">How can it be?</font>

648
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:42,610
<font color="yellow">This is a mere misunderstanding.</font>

649
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:45,940
<font color="yellow">It's a conspiracy and defamation. Someone's plotting against me.</font>

650
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:48,640
<font color="yellow">This is all Ms. Jang's fault.</font>

651
00:41:02,910 --> 00:41:04,510
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

652
00:41:05,070 --> 00:41:07,540
<font color="yellow">What happened? What is this?</font>

653
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:09,780
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

654
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:12,440
<font color="yellow">What are you going to do?</font>

655
00:41:13,340 --> 00:41:15,810
<font color="yellow">Do you know how much this car is?</font>

656
00:41:15,870 --> 00:41:18,910
<font color="yellow">I bought it with 36-month installment plan.</font>

657
00:41:18,910 --> 00:41:21,710
<font color="yellow">I still have 28 months to go. It's a new car.</font>

658
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:25,340
<font color="yellow">He's making a fuss.</font>

659
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:29,240
<font color="yellow">Wait, I thought I was supposed to pile up the bricks there.</font>

660
00:41:29,310 --> 00:41:30,670
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't pile up the bricks here.</font>

661
00:41:31,110 --> 00:41:34,640
<font color="yellow">Why would you pile up the bricks here?</font>

662
00:41:36,540 --> 00:41:38,170
<font color="yellow">What am I going to do?</font>

663
00:41:42,140 --> 00:41:43,310
<font color="yellow">I apologize.</font>

664
00:41:43,780 --> 00:41:44,910
<font color="yellow">Is that all?</font>

665
00:41:45,940 --> 00:41:47,210
<font color="yellow">How are you going to fix this?</font>

666
00:41:48,240 --> 00:41:50,440
<font color="yellow">We'll compensate for the damage.</font>

667
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:52,710
<font color="yellow">I don't care about the compensation.</font>

668
00:41:53,070 --> 00:41:56,010
<font color="yellow">How are you going to fix my car?</font>

669
00:41:58,140 --> 00:41:59,310
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

670
00:42:19,570 --> 00:42:20,710
<font color="yellow">Are you feeling better?</font>

671
00:42:22,280 --> 00:42:23,310
<font color="yellow">A little.</font>

672
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:27,710
<font color="yellow">That's why you shouldn't study too hard.</font>

673
00:42:28,110 --> 00:42:29,310
<font color="yellow">You know I can't.</font>

674
00:42:30,370 --> 00:42:31,440
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

675
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:34,940
<font color="yellow">But,</font>

676
00:42:36,010 --> 00:42:37,670
<font color="yellow">let's try our best, okay?</font>

677
00:42:40,970 --> 00:42:42,070
<font color="yellow">Have your meal.</font>

678
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:45,340
<font color="yellow">Look at you.</font>

679
00:42:45,810 --> 00:42:47,440
<font color="yellow">I didn't know you were eating.</font>

680
00:42:49,140 --> 00:42:50,370
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

681
00:42:50,810 --> 00:42:51,870
<font color="yellow">Did you sleep well?</font>

682
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:53,870
<font color="yellow">Yes?</font>

683
00:42:53,970 --> 00:42:57,740
<font color="yellow">Maybe it's the sleep. You look much better.</font>

684
00:42:57,740 --> 00:42:58,910
<font color="yellow">Right, Min Seok?</font>

685
00:43:02,910 --> 00:43:05,040
<font color="yellow">I'm glad it's nothing serious.</font>

686
00:43:05,310 --> 00:43:06,440
<font color="yellow">Thanks to Min Seok,</font>

687
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:08,910
<font color="yellow">you'll get better.</font>

688
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:12,940
<font color="yellow">I brought you a gift.</font>

689
00:43:13,440 --> 00:43:17,170
<font color="yellow">I understand it must have been hard for you to study.</font>

690
00:43:17,370 --> 00:43:19,840
<font color="yellow">I bought you something you like.</font>

691
00:43:21,070 --> 00:43:22,310
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

692
00:43:23,670 --> 00:43:25,210
<font color="yellow">It's the headphone...</font>

693
00:43:25,940 --> 00:43:27,070
<font color="yellow">you wanted to have.</font>

694
00:43:28,240 --> 00:43:30,970
<font color="yellow">You don't like when I listen to music.</font>

695
00:43:32,780 --> 00:43:35,610
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't listen to music for long.</font>

696
00:43:35,940 --> 00:43:38,140
<font color="yellow">You can listen to it once in a while,</font>

697
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:41,340
<font color="yellow">but not too long. You know what I mean, right?</font>

698
00:43:44,810 --> 00:43:47,840
<font color="yellow">But Ji Hoon, do you need to stay in the hospital?</font>

699
00:43:48,270 --> 00:43:49,340
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

700
00:43:50,570 --> 00:43:53,110
<font color="yellow">What do you mean? Where will he be if not here?</font>

701
00:43:53,110 --> 00:43:56,040
<font color="yellow">Min Seok, I want to him discharged today.</font>

702
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:57,940
<font color="yellow">No way. He can't be discharged.</font>

703
00:43:58,270 --> 00:44:00,240
<font color="yellow">If he can sit up and eat,</font>

704
00:44:00,310 --> 00:44:02,310
<font color="yellow">- he is recovered. - Hee Sook.</font>

705
00:44:02,910 --> 00:44:05,740
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon, there's an important exam, tomorrow.</font>

706
00:44:06,140 --> 00:44:08,210
<font color="yellow">Remember the boarding academy that I talked out before?</font>

707
00:44:08,210 --> 00:44:10,440
<font color="yellow">The one you were supposed to go during the winter break.</font>

708
00:44:10,740 --> 00:44:14,640
<font color="yellow">It became a competitive academy to get in. You have to take a test.</font>

709
00:44:14,840 --> 00:44:17,570
<font color="yellow">But do you know why it became competitive?</font>

710
00:44:18,140 --> 00:44:20,340
<font color="yellow">The students who studied there...</font>

711
00:44:20,340 --> 00:44:22,710
<font color="yellow">all went to either Seoul National University or KAIST.</font>

712
00:44:22,710 --> 00:44:24,010
<font color="yellow">- That's why you should... - Come outside.</font>

713
00:44:25,110 --> 00:44:27,670
<font color="yellow">- Come outside. - What are you doing?</font>

714
00:44:28,210 --> 00:44:29,210
<font color="yellow">Min Seok.</font>

715
00:44:29,370 --> 00:44:30,540
<font color="yellow">Come here.</font>

716
00:44:34,710 --> 00:44:35,770
<font color="yellow">Min Seok.</font>

717
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:38,870
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

718
00:44:39,070 --> 00:44:40,840
<font color="yellow">Are you out of your mind?</font>

719
00:44:40,840 --> 00:44:43,410
<font color="yellow">How can you think of taking him home when he hasn't fully recovered?</font>

720
00:44:43,410 --> 00:44:44,610
<font color="yellow">He has recovered.</font>

721
00:44:44,710 --> 00:44:46,670
<font color="yellow">Do you think he's recovered?</font>

722
00:44:46,670 --> 00:44:50,440
<font color="yellow">He hasn't? Look at him. He's sitting up and eating.</font>

723
00:44:53,610 --> 00:44:54,670
<font color="yellow">Min Seok.</font>

724
00:44:55,070 --> 00:44:58,410
<font color="yellow">It's an important time for Ji Hoon.</font>

725
00:44:58,510 --> 00:45:00,570
<font color="yellow">He doesn't have time to be in the hospital.</font>

726
00:45:00,870 --> 00:45:05,170
<font color="yellow">If he doesn't get into that academy, he won't get into the gifted school.</font>

727
00:45:13,970 --> 00:45:17,710
<font color="yellow">What's the point when your son isn't well?</font>

728
00:45:17,710 --> 00:45:20,440
<font color="yellow">You can still raise him well without sending him to that school.</font>

729
00:45:21,040 --> 00:45:22,170
<font color="yellow">Min Seok.</font>

730
00:45:23,570 --> 00:45:26,510
<font color="yellow">You're talking like this because he isn't your son.</font>

731
00:45:26,970 --> 00:45:28,170
<font color="yellow">How about you, Min Seok?</font>

732
00:45:28,440 --> 00:45:31,610
<font color="yellow">You sent your three daughters to a boarding school in the States.</font>

733
00:45:31,670 --> 00:45:33,870
<font color="yellow">You send them millions of dollars for their education.</font>

734
00:45:33,940 --> 00:45:36,970
<font color="yellow">How could you talk to me like this?</font>

735
00:45:37,410 --> 00:45:40,610
<font color="yellow">You don't even live with your wife for your children's education.</font>

736
00:45:40,610 --> 00:45:42,310
<font color="yellow">There's a reason to it.</font>

737
00:45:42,310 --> 00:45:43,510
<font color="yellow">I have my reasons, too.</font>

738
00:45:44,110 --> 00:45:45,240
<font color="yellow">Did you forget?</font>

739
00:45:45,770 --> 00:45:47,770
<font color="yellow">How our father treated us differently?</font>

740
00:45:48,040 --> 00:45:52,010
<font color="yellow">I'm not going to raise my son like he raised me.</font>

741
00:45:58,140 --> 00:46:01,110
<font color="yellow">It's a very important exam.</font>

742
00:46:01,410 --> 00:46:05,010
<font color="yellow">He can just go for a day tomorrow.</font>

743
00:46:05,010 --> 00:46:07,370
<font color="yellow">No, he can't. You can't take him there.</font>

744
00:46:09,370 --> 00:46:11,940
<font color="yellow">No, I will. He's my son.</font>

745
00:46:12,770 --> 00:46:14,040
<font color="yellow">Don't get involved.</font>

746
00:46:15,140 --> 00:46:16,370
<font color="yellow">Hee Sook.</font>

747
00:46:31,210 --> 00:46:32,270
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

748
00:46:32,610 --> 00:46:35,710
<font color="yellow">If this is what you want, you can stay here tonight.</font>

749
00:46:36,240 --> 00:46:39,540
<font color="yellow">But I'll bring you textbooks and study materials.</font>

750
00:46:39,810 --> 00:46:41,810
<font color="yellow">You'll prepare for the exam here,</font>

751
00:46:42,210 --> 00:46:44,210
<font color="yellow">and I'll drive you to the academy for the exam tomorrow.</font>

752
00:46:47,210 --> 00:46:48,510
<font color="yellow">Rest. I'll be back soon.</font>

753
00:47:12,740 --> 00:47:13,910
<font color="yellow">Hooray!</font>

754
00:47:24,170 --> 00:47:25,370
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

755
00:47:25,570 --> 00:47:27,140
<font color="yellow">Hi, Chang Soo.</font>

756
00:47:27,670 --> 00:47:29,340
<font color="yellow">Are you here to see Ji Hoon?</font>

757
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:31,710
<font color="yellow">Yes. I won these two dolls.</font>

758
00:47:31,710 --> 00:47:33,340
<font color="yellow">I want to give them to Ji Hoon.</font>

759
00:47:34,510 --> 00:47:35,770
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

760
00:47:36,910 --> 00:47:39,170
<font color="yellow">Gosh, it looks just like you.</font>

761
00:47:40,210 --> 00:47:41,370
<font color="yellow">I think so, too.</font>

762
00:47:50,570 --> 00:47:52,610
<font color="yellow">Why is it so hard?</font>

763
00:47:53,270 --> 00:47:55,570
<font color="yellow">His parents give him food, shelter, and they pay for his school.</font>

764
00:47:56,170 --> 00:47:58,510
<font color="yellow">The least he can do is listen to his parents.</font>

765
00:47:59,710 --> 00:48:02,910
<font color="yellow">The nurses here listen to what you say, right?</font>

766
00:48:03,170 --> 00:48:04,370
<font color="yellow">Why would they do that?</font>

767
00:48:04,740 --> 00:48:07,110
<font color="yellow">It's because you pay their salaries.</font>

768
00:48:07,570 --> 00:48:09,570
<font color="yellow">His parents do all that stuff for him.</font>

769
00:48:09,870 --> 00:48:11,540
<font color="yellow">Then he should listen to them.</font>

770
00:48:12,410 --> 00:48:15,770
<font color="yellow">If he doesn't want to, he should go out and live by himself.</font>

771
00:48:16,910 --> 00:48:20,010
<font color="yellow">- You rascal. - He receives his Mom's help.</font>

772
00:48:20,840 --> 00:48:22,710
<font color="yellow">It's ridiculous that...</font>

773
00:48:22,970 --> 00:48:25,110
<font color="yellow">he doesn't listen to such a good mom.</font>

774
00:48:28,240 --> 00:48:29,440
<font color="yellow">You do well at school, don't you?</font>

775
00:48:35,040 --> 00:48:36,410
<font color="yellow">Please don't ask me that.</font>

776
00:48:37,610 --> 00:48:39,440
<font color="yellow">Anyway, I hope...</font>

777
00:48:39,970 --> 00:48:41,810
<font color="yellow">you'd help Ji Hoon.</font>

778
00:48:43,940 --> 00:48:46,640
<font color="yellow">I won't be a good help to him.</font>

779
00:48:48,570 --> 00:48:50,370
<font color="yellow">It's not like I can switch our moms.</font>

780
00:48:53,510 --> 00:48:54,740
<font color="yellow">Poor Ji Hoon.</font>

781
00:48:54,940 --> 00:48:58,070
<font color="yellow">If it was as simple as class duty, I'd switch them for him.</font>

782
00:49:16,110 --> 00:49:17,940
<font color="yellow">Dr. Kang.</font>

783
00:49:18,940 --> 00:49:21,440
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon disappeared.</font>

784
00:49:21,440 --> 00:49:22,610
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

785
00:49:35,740 --> 00:49:36,740
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon!</font>

786
00:49:41,570 --> 00:49:43,240
<font color="yellow">What should we do, Dr. Kang?</font>

787
00:49:44,210 --> 00:49:45,340
<font color="yellow">Let's check that side.</font>

788
00:49:47,640 --> 00:49:49,140
<font color="yellow">- Ji Hoon. - Ji Hoon.</font>

789
00:49:58,540 --> 00:50:00,610
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon. What should I do?</font>

790
00:50:02,570 --> 00:50:04,070
<font color="yellow">- He's not there? - He's not.</font>

791
00:50:27,210 --> 00:50:29,210
<font color="yellow">- What should we do? - Please come down.</font>

792
00:50:31,310 --> 00:50:33,010
<font color="yellow">Please don't do that.</font>

793
00:50:34,010 --> 00:50:35,070
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon!</font>

794
00:50:36,270 --> 00:50:38,440
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon. Why are you doing this?</font>

795
00:50:38,610 --> 00:50:41,210
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing? Come down at once.</font>

796
00:50:42,270 --> 00:50:43,310
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon!</font>

797
00:50:47,110 --> 00:50:48,110
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

798
00:50:49,610 --> 00:50:51,540
<font color="yellow">I don't want to live any more.</font>

799
00:50:52,070 --> 00:50:55,670
<font color="yellow">Come down first. We'll talk after you come down.</font>

800
00:50:56,170 --> 00:50:57,740
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't do this.</font>

801
00:50:58,670 --> 00:51:02,510
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon. Please calm down, and get down here. Ji Hoon.</font>

802
00:51:02,770 --> 00:51:03,810
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

803
00:51:04,440 --> 00:51:06,410
<font color="yellow">You understood me,</font>

804
00:51:07,670 --> 00:51:09,810
<font color="yellow">but I don't think I can hold out any longer.</font>

805
00:51:09,810 --> 00:51:10,870
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon.</font>

806
00:51:10,870 --> 00:51:12,410
<font color="yellow">Mom wants me to go to a boarding school.</font>

807
00:51:12,740 --> 00:51:14,410
<font color="yellow">Do you know what people do there?</font>

808
00:51:15,170 --> 00:51:18,410
<font color="yellow">They study all day every day.</font>

809
00:51:18,770 --> 00:51:21,110
<font color="yellow">I will...</font>

810
00:51:22,040 --> 00:51:24,010
<font color="yellow">convince your mom, okay?</font>

811
00:51:24,640 --> 00:51:27,840
<font color="yellow">- So please come down here. - That's not going to work.</font>

812
00:51:28,440 --> 00:51:29,870
<font color="yellow">She will kill me.</font>

813
00:51:30,410 --> 00:51:33,270
<font color="yellow">She will send me to a boarding school and kill me eventually.</font>

814
00:51:34,870 --> 00:51:37,010
<font color="yellow">Rather than dying while being forced to study,</font>

815
00:51:37,440 --> 00:51:39,410
<font color="yellow">I'll just kill myself instead.</font>

816
00:51:40,440 --> 00:51:42,910
<font color="yellow">- Watch out! - Don't come near me.</font>

817
00:51:43,410 --> 00:51:45,710
<font color="yellow">I will kill myself! I'll do it!</font>

818
00:51:54,640 --> 00:51:56,640
<font color="yellow">Let go of me! I will kill myself.</font>

819
00:51:56,640 --> 00:51:58,970
<font color="yellow">- Ji Hoon. It's okay. - I want to die! I'm going to die!</font>

820
00:51:59,210 --> 00:52:01,440
<font color="yellow">- Calm down. - Let me go.</font>

821
00:52:02,370 --> 00:52:03,370
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon!</font>

822
00:52:03,870 --> 00:52:05,440
<font color="yellow">- No. - Get off of me!</font>

823
00:52:05,440 --> 00:52:06,940
<font color="yellow">Calm down, Ji Hoon!</font>

824
00:52:06,940 --> 00:52:09,670
<font color="yellow">- Let me go. - Ji Hoon!</font>

825
00:52:09,670 --> 00:52:13,340
<font color="yellow">- Ji Hoon. - Please calm down, Ji Hoon!</font>

826
00:52:15,340 --> 00:52:18,210
<font color="yellow">How could you forget to buy the pork?</font>

827
00:52:18,940 --> 00:52:21,840
<font color="yellow">You should buy the pork first before you buy napa cabbage.</font>

828
00:52:22,340 --> 00:52:24,770
<font color="yellow">Why bother make kimchi for winter? We don't even have pork.</font>

829
00:52:24,770 --> 00:52:26,740
<font color="yellow">Why would I make kimchi without pork?</font>

830
00:52:27,310 --> 00:52:30,270
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Mother. I forgot to buy it. I'm so sorry.</font>

831
00:52:31,310 --> 00:52:33,970
<font color="yellow">There're things you must not forget.</font>

832
00:52:33,970 --> 00:52:36,440
<font color="yellow">You know the things I like.</font>

833
00:52:36,440 --> 00:52:38,710
<font color="yellow">How could you forget to buy it?</font>

834
00:52:38,870 --> 00:52:40,740
<font color="yellow">I guess I've been too lenient.</font>

835
00:52:40,770 --> 00:52:43,210
<font color="yellow">Not at all, Mother. That's not true.</font>

836
00:52:43,210 --> 00:52:45,370
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Mother. Please forgive me.</font>

837
00:52:45,610 --> 00:52:48,410
<font color="yellow">Freshly made kimchi with...</font>

838
00:52:48,410 --> 00:52:51,610
<font color="yellow">softly boiled pork,</font>

839
00:52:52,210 --> 00:52:53,970
<font color="yellow">a little oyster,</font>

840
00:52:54,070 --> 00:52:57,210
<font color="yellow">and a bit of pickled shrimp wrapped together.</font>

841
00:52:57,210 --> 00:53:01,040
<font color="yellow">You know how much I love to eat it.</font>

842
00:53:01,540 --> 00:53:03,770
<font color="yellow">Imagining it makes me want to eat it even more.</font>

843
00:53:04,440 --> 00:53:05,640
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry.</font>

844
00:53:05,670 --> 00:53:08,710
<font color="yellow">I guess I did get old. Please forgive me.</font>

845
00:53:09,740 --> 00:53:13,040
<font color="yellow">I can never let this slide, Jeong Ae!</font>

846
00:53:13,110 --> 00:53:16,140
<font color="yellow">- Starting from today... - Mother, please.</font>

847
00:53:16,140 --> 00:53:19,240
